# ╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
# ║  WARNING: Copy to .env.local and fill in real values. Never commit .env.local.
# ║  StreamPay Clarinet / Smart Contract Environment Variables
# ║                                                                              ║
# ║  ⚠️  DEPLOYER_MNEMONIC contains your wallet seed phrase.                     ║
# ║      NEVER commit real values. Compromised mnemonics = stolen funds.         ║
# ╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Deployer Wallet Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# 24-word BIP-39 mnemonic phrase for the deployer wallet (Required)
# Format: 24 space-separated words
# Generate with: clarinet new or any BIP-39 compatible wallet
#
# ███████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████
# ██  CRITICAL: This is your wallet seed phrase. Anyone with access to this    ██
# ██  mnemonic can drain all funds from the wallet. NEVER:                     ██
# ██  - Commit real values to git                                               ██
# ██  - Share in chat, email, or bug reports                                   ██
# ██  - Store in plaintext files outside of .env.local                         ██
# ██  - Use a mainnet-funded wallet for development                            ██
# ███████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████████
#
DEPLOYER_MNEMONIC=

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Network Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Target Stacks network for deployment (Required)
# Values: devnet | testnet | mainnet
# NOTE: Start with devnet, promote to testnet, only mainnet after full audit
STACKS_NETWORK=devnet

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Clarity Language Configuration
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Clarity language version (Required)
# Values: 1 | 2 | 3
# NOTE: StreamPay uses Clarity 2 for enhanced features
CLARITY_VERSION=2
